</PRE>
<DL>
<DT><B>All Implemented Interfaces:</B> <DD><A HREF="../../../../../org/springframework/core/Ordered.html" title="interface in org.springframework.core">Ordered</A>, <A HREF="../../../../../org/springframework/web/portlet/HandlerExceptionResolver.html" title="interface in org.springframework.web.portlet">HandlerExceptionResolver</A></DD>
